name: BetaPro S&P/TSX 60 -2x Daily Bear ETF
longDescription: CNDD seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the S and P/TSX 60 TM Index. CNDD does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
